  "title": "Our Research",
  "excerpt": "<p>Our Research At Armstrong Capital, our pride lies in the depth and precision of our research, a cornerstone that distinguishes us and instills trust in our clients. We adhere to a comprehensive, two-sided research approach within the wealth management industry, setting the stage for informed financial planning. Our Research: Empowering Smart Financial Decisions At Armstrong [&hellip;]</p>\n",
  "content": "\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"5526\" class=\"elementor elementor-5526\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-dcb9a0f elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-stretched how-we-work-custom research-page elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"dcb9a0f\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6999da6\" data-id=\"6999da6\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-aa11023 text-center elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"aa11023\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-08c5c39\" data-id=\"08c5c39\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-edbcc09 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_hero_title\" data-id=\"edbcc09\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_hero_title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n    <div class=\"te-box-title sec-title \">        \n        \t\t<h2 class=\"te_title counsolve-size-default\">Our Research</h2>        \n                <div class=\"normal__text text-box\">\n            <p><p>At Armstrong Capital, our pride lies in the depth and precision of our research, a cornerstone that</p><p>distinguishes us and instills trust in our clients. We adhere to a comprehensive, two-sided research approach within the wealth</p><p>management industry, setting the stage for informed financial planning.</p></p>\n        </div>\n                \n    </div>     \n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2bfd16d e-grid e-con-full e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2bfd16d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0721dd5 research-section-box elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_hero_title\" data-id=\"0721dd5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_hero_title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n    <div class=\"te-box-title sec-title \">        \n        \t\t<h2 class=\"te_title counsolve-size-default\">Our Research: Empowering Smart Financial Decisions</h2>        \n                <div class=\"normal__text text-box\">\n            <p><p>At Armstrong Capital, our research combines precision, innovation, and foresight to empower confident financial decisions. Through cutting-edge analysis and continuous market monitoring, we deliver strategies tailored to your goals, adapting seamlessly to evolving market dynamics for consistent, goal-focused results.</p><ul><li><strong>Comprehensive Analysis:</strong> Rigorous evaluations ensure every investment aligns perfectly with your financial goals.</li><li><strong>Proactive Strategies</strong>: Anticipating market shifts, we keep your portfolio ahead of the curve.</li><li><strong>Dynamic Updates</strong>: Quarterly reviews refine recommendations, maximizing potential and ensuring ongoing relevance.</li></ul></p>\n        </div>\n                \n    </div>     \n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-584cc84 research-section-box elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_hero_title\" data-id=\"584cc84\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_hero_title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n    <div class=\"te-box-title sec-title \">        \n        \t\t<h2 class=\"te_title counsolve-size-default\">The White List: A Symbol of Excellence</h2>        \n                <div class=\"normal__text text-box\">\n            <p><p>At Armstrong Capital, our proprietary White List reflects our dedication to meticulous research and top-tier fund selection. It’s more than a curated list, it’s a symbol of trust, designed to help you confidently grow and protect your wealth.</p><ul><li><strong>Data-Driven Selection</strong>: We analyze funds using a bottom-up approach, focusing on factors like risk-adjusted returns, fund manager expertise, and market trends. ensuring top-tier performance and stability.</li><li><strong>Dynamic Monitoring</strong>: Quarterly evaluations keep funds aligned with market trends and clients' financial goals.</li><li><strong>Diverse Options</strong>: A balanced mix of traditional and alternative investments tailored to unique client profiles.</li></ul></p>\n        </div>\n                \n    </div>     \n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b449f08 research-section-box elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_hero_title\" data-id=\"b449f08\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_hero_title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n    <div class=\"te-box-title sec-title \">        \n        \t\t<h2 class=\"te_title counsolve-size-default\">Model Portfolios: Consistent, Innovative Investment Strategies</h2>        \n                <div class=\"normal__text text-box\">\n            <p><p>At Armstrong Capital, we pride ourselves on creating model portfolios that deliver standardized, yet highly effective investment strategies tailored to diverse financial scenarios.</p><ul><li><strong>Strategic Framework</strong>: Our model portfolios provide a consistent investment structure, ensuring reliable outcomes across diverse scenarios.</li><li><strong>Diversified and Adaptive:</strong> Designed with balanced asset allocation, they address specific goals like wealth creation or retirement, catering to varied risk profiles.</li><li><strong>Research-Driven Excellence</strong>: Backed by robust research, portfolios are regularly updated to align with market trends and maximize returns.</li></ul></p>\n        </div>\n                \n    </div>     \n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-940c3d2 e-grid text-center e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"940c3d2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-541a758 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_hero_title\" data-id=\"541a758\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_hero_title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n    <div class=\"te-box-title sec-title \">        \n                <span class=\"te-subtitle sub-title\"><span class=\"te-bn-subtitle\">Equity Fund Research</span></span>\n        \t\t<h2 class=\"te_title counsolve-size-small\">When analyzing equity mutual funds, we rely on critical metrics to provide recommendations grounded in robust, data-driven insights</h2>        \n                \n    </div>     \n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-076dc07 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"076dc07\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fe72a84\" data-id=\"fe72a84\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-b96f808 nri-what-do-area elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"b96f808\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-7b46de7\" data-id=\"7b46de7\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1743d9a elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_feature_image_box\" data-id=\"1743d9a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_feature_image_box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n        \n    <div class=\"left-column town-feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-content\">\n            <div class=\"chooseus-block-one\">\n                <div class=\"inner-box\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box town-quote-icon\">\n                    \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\" flaticon-knowledge\"></i>                                                \n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"static-content\">\n                        <div class=\"town-title\"><h3>Active Ratios</h3></div>\n                        <div class=\"town-text\"><p>We prioritize performance ratios like Alpha, Beta, Sharpe Ratio, Turnover, and R-Squared to evaluate a fund’s potential.</p></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"overlay-content town-text\">\n                        <p>We prioritize performance ratios like Alpha, Beta, Sharpe Ratio, Turnover, and R-Squared to evaluate a fund’s potential.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n    \t</div>\n    </div>       \n\t        \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-18710ce elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_feature_image_box\" data-id=\"18710ce\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_feature_image_box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n        \n    <div class=\"left-column town-feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-content\">\n            <div class=\"chooseus-block-one\">\n                <div class=\"inner-box\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box town-quote-icon\">\n                    \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\" flaticon-united\"></i>                                                \n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"static-content\">\n                        <div class=\"town-title\"><h3>Portfolio Overlap</h3></div>\n                        <div class=\"town-text\"><p>Our analysis minimizes stock overlap, ensuring diversification by avoiding funds with significant common holdings within a portfolio.</p></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"overlay-content town-text\">\n                        <p>Our analysis minimizes stock overlap, ensuring diversification by avoiding funds with significant common holdings within a portfolio.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n    \t</div>\n    </div>       \n\t        \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b48cdf7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_feature_image_box\" data-id=\"b48cdf7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_feature_image_box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n        \n    <div class=\"left-column town-feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-content\">\n            <div class=\"chooseus-block-one\">\n                <div class=\"inner-box\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box town-quote-icon\">\n                    \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\" flaticon-meeting\"></i>                                                \n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"static-content\">\n                        <div class=\"town-title\"><h3>Fund Manager Scorecard</h3></div>\n                        <div class=\"town-text\"><p>We assess the fund manager's history, style, and ability to identify multibagger stocks, ensuring consistent fund performance.</p></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"overlay-content town-text\">\n                        <p>We assess the fund manager's history, style, and ability to identify multibagger stocks, ensuring consistent fund performance.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n    \t</div>\n    </div>       \n\t        \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-78fddda\" data-id=\"78fddda\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b31d74f elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_image_widget\" data-id=\"b31d74f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_image_widget.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                \r\n        <!-- chooseus-section -->\r\n        <section class=\"chooseus-section town-image-box p-0 m-0\">\r\n            <div class=\"image-box town-image-box\">\r\n                <figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/chooseus-1.png\" alt=\"Awesome Image\"></figure>\r\n                <div class=\"image-shape\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/shape-8.png\" alt=\"Awesome Image\"></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </section>        \r\n        \r\n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-bfaec8e\" data-id=\"bfaec8e\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8eb06f0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_feature_image_box\" data-id=\"8eb06f0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_feature_image_box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n        \n    <div class=\"right-column town-feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-content\">\n            <div class=\"chooseus-block-one\">\n                <div class=\"inner-box\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box town-quote-icon\">\n                    \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\" flaticon-risk-management\"></i>                                                \n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"static-content\">\n                        <div class=\"town-title\"><h3>Stock Range</h3></div>\n                        <div class=\"town-text\"><p>We shortlist funds holding a diversified portfolio of 40 to 70 stocks, balancing risk and return effectively.</p></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"overlay-content town-text\">\n                        <p>We shortlist funds holding a diversified portfolio of 40 to 70 stocks, balancing risk and return effectively.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n    \t</div>\n    </div>\n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef21b3b elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_feature_image_box\" data-id=\"ef21b3b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_feature_image_box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n        \n    <div class=\"right-column town-feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-content\">\n            <div class=\"chooseus-block-one\">\n                <div class=\"inner-box\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box town-quote-icon\">\n                    \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\" flaticon-monitor\"></i>                                                \n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"static-content\">\n                        <div class=\"town-title\"><h3>Fund Metrics</h3></div>\n                        <div class=\"town-text\"><p>Our criteria focus on higher active ratios, a strong SIP book, and lower Asset Under Management for better fund selection.</p></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"overlay-content town-text\">\n                        <p>Our criteria focus on higher active ratios, a strong SIP book, and lower Asset Under Management for better fund selection.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n    \t</div>\n    </div>\n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db3b117 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_feature_image_box\" data-id=\"db3b117\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_feature_image_box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n        \n    <div class=\"right-column town-feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-content\">\n            <div class=\"chooseus-block-one\">\n                <div class=\"inner-box\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box town-quote-icon\">\n                    \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\" flaticon-advice\"></i>                                                \n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"static-content\">\n                        <div class=\"town-title\"><h3>Fund Performance</h3></div>\n                        <div class=\"town-text\"><p>We evaluate fund resilience by analyzing volatility, recovery during market upswings, and reduced decline during downturns.</p></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"overlay-content town-text\">\n                        <p>We evaluate fund resilience by analyzing volatility, recovery during market upswings, and reduced decline during downturns.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n    \t</div>\n    </div>\n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t",
